      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for a pre-owned vehicle. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior finish is breathtaking, boasting a deep, glass-like luster with absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Step inside to an interior that remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creasing or bolster wear, still retaining that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and digital interface functions with crisp, tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians\u2014full service records are meticulously organized and included. The car sits on pristine alloy wheels with zero curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread depth. This is a rare find for the discerning buyer who demands perfection without compromise. No accidents, no smokers, and no stories\u2014just an immaculate driving machine ready for its next caretaker.",
